the tangent vector

00:01:46.330 --> 00:01:47.890
to that world line.

00:01:47.890 --> 00:01:50.350
And I forgot to put
the physics up here.

00:01:50.350 --> 00:01:52.840
The key reason why
this is interesting

00:01:52.840 --> 00:01:57.445
