means you are

00:02:07.980 --> 00:02:11.730
moving under the influence
of nothing but gravity.

00:02:11.730 --> 00:02:15.240
And if you want to
understand gravity

00:02:15.240 --> 00:02:17.670
in a relativistic theory, well,
that's all you care about.

00:02:17.670 --> 00:02:20.040
So these are very
important trajectories.

00:02:20.040 --> 00:02:23.490
And you know, it's
not an exaggeration

00:02:23.490 --> 00:02:28.020
to say that solving
this equation, OK-- so

00:02:28.020 --> 00:02:30.930
in this thing, I've kind of left
