01:09:08.859 --> 01:09:09.359
But look.

01:09:09.359 --> 01:09:11.883
Both mu and nu
are dummy indices.

01:09:11.883 --> 01:09:13.300
They're dummy
indices, so what I'm

01:09:13.300 --> 01:09:22.069
going to do is-- on the last
